Check Keyword Data
    [Arguments]    ${kw}    ${name}    ${assign}=    ${args}=    ${status}=PASS    ${tags}=
    Should be equal    ${kw.name}    ${name}
    Should be equal    ${kw.status}    ${status}
    ${kwassign}=    Catenate    SEPARATOR=,${SPACE}    @{kw.assign}
    Should be equal    ${kwassign}    ${assign}
